                    💼 Built by <a class="text-light small" href="mailto:thomas@tsmithcode.ai">Thomas Smith</a> ·
                    <a class="text-light" href="https://tsmithcode.ai" target="_blank">tsmithcode.ai</a> 🐙  <a class="text-light" href="/github.com/tsmithcode/slitting-efficiency-dashboard">GitHub</a>
                    
